                                        1844</bibl>, <ref target="https://www.e-rara.ch/6872998">II.3, 295</ref>; <bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/RQ7INXBQ">Humboldt 2009a</bibl>, 59; <bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/2D3VTWKZ">Honigmann 1982</bibl>,
                                    193–195; <bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/UQGSA7CH">Brand
